This repository follows the requirements of the Coursera course "Getting and Cleaning data", the fourth component of the Data Science specialization. About the raw data

The original dataset is Human Activity Recognition Using Smartphones Data Set. The data was obtained from http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones

The data was downloaded, merged according to Subject, Activity, and Features, before all these are merged into one big dataset. 
Then the descriptive activity names were given to name the activities in the data set, and exported. 

